# Credits

## Original Artwork

All artwork in this repository was created by **Daniel Cook** and is generously
provided to the community through his Lost Garden website.

- **Artist:** Daniel Cook
- **Website:** https://lostgarden.com/
- **Original Bundle:** [Iron Plague (Sinistar) Graphics](https://lostgarden.com/2005/03/30/download-a-complete-set-of-sweet-8-bit-sinistar-clone-graphics/)
- **License:** [Creative Commons Attribution 3.0](https://lostgarden.com/2007/03/15/lost-garden-license/)

## About This Repository

This repository contains a repackaged and reorganized version of Daniel Cook's
"Iron Plague (Sinistar)" art bundle. The original BMP sprite sheets have been
extracted into individual PNG files with consistent naming conventions to make
them easier to use in game development projects.

**To be absolutely clear:** The maintainer of this repository claims **no
ownership, rights, or copyright** to any of the artwork contained herein. All
artistic work belongs solely to Daniel Cook. This repository simply provides
cleaned-up organization and tooling to make these freely-licensed assets more
accessible to developers.

## Attribution Requirements

If you use these assets in your project, please include attribution to the
original artist:

```
[Your Game Title] art by Daniel Cook (Lostgarden.com)
```

## Thank You

A huge thank you to Daniel Cook for creating these wonderful assets and sharing
them with the indie game development community. Your generosity has helped
countless developers bring their creative visions to life.
